headline.main: No. 18 DePaul Women Beat Seton Hall in Big East Tournament
headline.print_headline: No. 18 DePaul Women Beat Seton Hall in Big East Tournament

lead_paragraph: Chante Stonewall had a career-high 20 points, Brooke Schulte scored all of her 16 points in the first half and No. 18 DePaul cruised to a 92-60 win over Seton Hall on Sunday night in the Big East Tournament.
